Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [matrix] <polycryptoblog:matrix.org> Notary nodes are a different form of self-funding governance. More akin to a republic than a democracy like in dash

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [matrix] <polycryptoblog:matrix.org> You elect the notaries who receive a certain amount of funds from easy difficulty mining.  Typically these notaries received votes based on campaign promises of what to do Funds in excess of labor/hardware/maintenance  .  The difference between the two systems is one you choose a delegate to work in what is in your interest,  the other is referendum.
